= install: =
python3 -m pip install --user -r requirements.txt
or
python3 -m pip install --user requests

= run: =
python3 main.py BIND_ADDRESS BIND_PORT HTTP_PROXY_SPEC

where HTTP_PROXY_SPEC is in form: http://user:pass@host:port

example:
sudo python3 main.py 127.0.0.1 80 http://localhost:3128

(sudo is required to listen on privilieged port 80)

